#REVIEWS

##New York Times
Desk Set was released in 1957 and received a [mixed review](http://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9D03E3D91631E63ABC4E52DFB366838C649EDE)

##Rotten Tomatoes
Although Desk Set has only received 19 critic reviews, it's [TOMATOMETER score](http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/desk_set/) is 100%

##IMDB
With more than _5,000_ reviews, Desk Set receives 7.3/10 stars. [_click here_](http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0050307/ratings?ref_=tt_ov_rt) to see the weighted average and demographic breakdowns

